com.feedzai.commons.sql.abstraction.engine

Class AbstractTranslator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.feedzai.commons.sql.abstraction.engine.AbstractTranslator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DB2Translator, H2Translator, MySqlTranslator, OracleTranslator, PostgreSqlTranslator, SqlServerTranslator

    public abstract class AbstractTranslator
extends Object
    Abstract translator to be extended by specific implementations.

    This class already provides translations that are common to all databases.

    Since:
    2.0.0
    Author:
    Rui Vilao (rui.vilao@feedzai.com)
